metadata.name: Lone King
metadata.description:
My guardian once told me to become a free soul who can stand on his own and so I did. I stand alone to be a king in my own world. I spread my territory with my sweat and blood. And I built my own castle on it.

However, lately I think that something is missing.
No, I'm sure I missed something.
Whatever that is...
